name: Focusrite Scarlett Solo 4th Gen USB Audio Interface, for the Guitarist, Vocalist, or Producer — High-Fidelity, Studio Quality Recording, and All the Software You Need to Record
small_description: The new generation of the songwriter's interface: Plug in your mic and guitar and let Scarlett Solo 4th Gen bring big studio sound to wherever you make music. - Studio-quality sound: With a huge 120dB dynamic range, the newest generation of Scarlett uses the same converters as Focusrite’s flagship interfaces, found in the world's biggest studios. - Find your signature sound: Scarlett 4th Gen's improved Air mode lifts vocals and guitars to the front of the mix, adding musical presence and rich harmonic drive to your recordings. - Everything you need to record, mix and master your music: Includes industry-leading recording software and a full collection of record-making plugins. - Easy Start: It’s never been easier to get recording with Scarlett 4th Gen. Focusrite’s tried-and-tested Easy Start tool will have you making music in minutes.
full_description: The newest generation of Scarlett Solo makes it easier than ever to record and release your songs. A detailed ultra-low-noise mic pre. Studio-grade converters, with a huge 120dB dynamic range that matches what you'd find in a pro studio. A complete songwriter's recording toolkit includes Pro Tools Artist, Ableton Live Lite, and Focusrite’s Hitmaker Expansion software bundle; featuring Auto-Tune Access for Vocals, Softube Marshall Silver Jubilee 2555 for guitar, Native Instruments MASSIVE synth and more. Air mode lets you record with all the character of a big studio console. Get great sound through any headphones from Solo’s amped-up headphone output with independent volume control. Personalised Easy Start, 24/7/365 Support and three-year warranty make sure Scarlett is ready whenever you are.

Perfect for lighting enhancement applications, night clubs, parties, mobile DJ's 1 2 3 What types of fog machines can Fog Worx be used with? Fog Worx can be used with any water based fog machines that are at least 400 watts. Will Fog Worx set off smoke detectors or sprinkler systems? Optical type smoke detectors can potentially go off since they sense the small water based particles as smoke. Sprinkler systems are not affected as they need heat to trigger the sensors. name: D'Addario Guitar Strings - Phosphor Bronze Acoustic Guitar Strings - EJ16-5P - Rich, Full Tonal Spectrum - For 6 String Guitars - 12-53 Light, 5-Pack
small_description: CORROSION-RESISTANT, PRECISION WOUND – D’Addario Phosphor Bronze acoustic guitar strings are precision wound with phosphor bronze wrap wire, over a hexagonal high-carbon steel core. - WARM, BALANCED TONE - Phosphor Bronze wrap wire provides tried-and-true D’Addario acoustic tone, with beautiful balance and warmth suitable for all musical genres. - MOST POPULAR ACOUSTIC GUITAR STRING - Now the standard in acoustic guitar strings, Phosphor Bronze strings were originally pioneered by D’Addario in the 1970s. - EARN REWARD POINTS - D’Addario Phosphor Bronze acoustic guitar strings come with a code on the recyclable VCI bag, which you can register to earn Players Circle points. - MADE IN THE USA – Our Phosphor Bronze strings are made in the USA—drawn to exacting specifications at our New York production facility.
full_description: D'Addario was the first to use Phosphor Bronze in acoustic guitar strings back in 1974. Today, Phosphor Bronze is played throughout the world and considered to be the standard in acoustic strings, thanks to its beautiful sonic balance and tonal warmth. Our pioneering Phosphor Bronze acoustic guitar strings are precision wound with phosphor bronze wrap wire over a high-carbon steel core, providing tonal versatility suitable for all acoustic styles and musical genres. 12-53 Light gauge strings are our most popular acoustic gauge, providing a nice balance of playability and tone.

small_description: New 2024 Model with Crystal Clear Audio: Mini Mic Pro utilizes state-of-the-art Series V 2.4GHz digital transmission and proprietary near-zero latency codec with 128-bit encryption, it delivers crystal-clear, incredibly stable audio with a range of up to 260m. Please make sure the bluetooth in your cellphone is OFF before starting to make voice/video recordings. For Andriod devices, make sure to open OTG function before using.

full_description: The video showcases the product in use. The video guides you through product setup. The video compares multiple products. The video shows the product being unpacked.  1 Program Interview 2 Video Recording Will this works with my iphone case box? Or require me to remove case make this to fit? That's not necessary. If your phone case does not interfere with the use of the charger, it will not affect the microphone either. What is included in the box of this wireless microphone product? One receiver,two microphones,two plush microphone sleeves,four sponge microphone sleeves,one Type-C data cable and one instruction manual. What if my phone cannot pair with the wireless microphone for iPhone? Please unplug and Insert the receiver and pair again.If you still cannot pair, please open your phone lock screen,unplug and Insert the receiver. What system is this wireless microphone suitable for? Is it suitable for Android phones? The wireless microphone requires an IOS12 or higher system.Attention! This product is not suitable for Android! How to determine if the product is damaged or the system is outdated when the microphone is not working? Please go to [Settings] - [About Phone] on your phone to check if the word 'DOCK' exists? If it exists, it indicates that the link was successful. Please upgrade the system. If it does not exist, it indicates that the microphone is damaged.

name: Double Sided Tape Heavy Duty, Nano Double Sided Adhesive Tape, Clear Mounting Tape Picture Hanging Adhesive Strips (9.85FT)
small_description: 【Multifunctional EZlifego Nano-tech Tape】- By using the most advanced nano-technology, made of the latest acrylic gel material, our heavy duty two sided adhesive tape has incredibly strong adhesion and excellent durability. The excellent solution to all your DIY mounting project. - 【Easy to Use】- No Tools Required. Powerful 2-Way Bond capability makes objects firmly attached to any surface. Instant Bonding does not require curing or drying stage. It can be easily cut to any size or length you need, all you need to do is stick the tape to the surface of the item. - 【Traceless & Weatherproof】- This industrial strength super strong adhesive tape works great on almost any smooth surface indoors or outdoors, such as wall, tile, glass, plastic, metal, marble, ceramic, etc. - 【Diversified Uses to Meet All Your Needs】- Strong Holding Power can effectively mount or repair stuff without drilling hole or nails, fixing or pasting items such as picture hangers, frames, photos, festival decorations, wall paper stickers, posters, hooks, floating shelves, desk holders, carpets, power sockets, art crafts, board shelf, LED, DIY items, school & house room decor aesthetic and so on. - 【EZlifego Tape Is an Essential for Daily Life】- Join the 3 million+ powered by our leading technology, it will bring great convenience to your life! Using Tips: Be slow and careful during the removal step, our adhesive tape has strong viscosity, which may cause the wall surface to peel off during removal due the unstable nature of the painted wall.
full_description: IMPORTANT TROUBLE SHOOTING ： 1. Please Note: it is not recommended to use it on unstable Paint Walls，rough walls, powdery walls, wet surfaces or uneven surfaces. When using the tape on these surfaces due to strong adhesion and the nature of painted wall, which may peel off painted wall upon removal. 2. Before use -- Please keep the mounting surface dry, clean and free of oil when mounting to make instant and permanent bond and get great water and moisture resistance ability. After use -- Press down hard and hold for 20 seconds after sticking. Make sure the tape is firmly attached to the surface, this will help maintain long-lasting stickiness . 3.How to remove -- Step one: Separate the item from the surface to be pasted -- Gently move item left/right，up/down until the item separates from the surface. Step two: Peel off the tape from the item -- Using hot air from a hair dryer will soften the tape and make it easier to remove, then slowly peel the tape off the item. 4. Storing the tape in our 'reusable bag' can prevent the tape from sticking to the packaging box, making it easier to use next time. Then put the packaged tape into our 'packaging box' , which can effectively avoid direct sunlight and facilitate long-term storage. 5. To avoid possible damage, do not use the tape to hold heavy objects or valuables. 6. Keep this product out of the reach of children. 7. If the tape is directly exposed to sunlight for a prolonged period, the colour of the tape’s surface may turn yellow. full_description: HP Papers is a premium line of uncoated printing paper optimized to provide superior print paper performance when used with HP hardware and supplies and in all other makes and models of printing and copying equipment. Launched in 1996, HP Papers are manufactured and marketed exclusively worldwide in over 75 countries by Sylvamo, a globally recognized leader in paper products, under license from the Hewlett-Packard Company. With a diverse range of products designed to support a wide range of print applications, from everyday copies to full-color presentations, you can be assured of consistent, high-quality print performance every time. HP Copy&Print20 Paper is a 20 lb, super smooth, economical and multipurpose paper for everyday printing at home, at school and in the office. HP Copy&Print20 offers HP quality and reliability at a great value. Its ultra-white shade (92 bright, 155 whiteness) and ColorLok Technology provides brighter colors and bolder blacks for reports, school work and all general printing needs. HP Copy&Print20 printer paper is available in 8.5 x 11 letter size paper.
